title: Google\Cloud\VideoIntelligence\V1\LogoRecognitionAnnotation
name: LogoRecognitionAnnotation
description:

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.entity
params.description: Entity category information to specify the logo class that all the logo tracks within this LogoRecognitionAnnotation are recognized as.

params.name: data.tracks
params.description: All logo tracks where the recognized logo appears. Each track corresponds to one logo instance appearing in consecutive frames.

params.name: data.segments
params.description: All video segments where the recognized logo appears. There might be multiple instances of the same logo class appearing in one VideoSegment.
